{"tid":1183642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：實行垃圾分類　全社會一起努力改善生活環境","createTime":"2019-06-03T05:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T05:21:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d67f594e7e8af7130528d345137babec460a13ca","tid":1183642,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1460670_1_20190603130920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1460670_1_20190603130920.jpg&h=2774f7ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平近日對垃圾分類工作作出重要指示，強調實行垃圾分類，關係廣大人民群眾生活環境，關係節約使用資源，也是社會文明水平的一個重要體現。<br />\n<br />\n習近平指出，推行垃圾分類，關鍵是要加強科學管理、形成長效機制、推動習慣養成。要開展廣泛的教育引導工作，讓廣大人民群眾認識到實行垃圾分類的重要性和必要性，通過有效的督促引導，讓更多人培養垃圾分類的好習慣，全社會一起為改善生活環境作努力，一起來為綠色發展、可持續發展作貢獻。"},{"pid":"c3b8de4ff7c916ac753bb8382423fdc92254e3c3","tid":1183642,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:41:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460670-20190603.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460670-20190603.htm&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewONOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=534774e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460670-20190603.htm&h=22d8e73b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460670-20190603.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8edea2ec668507e5d4ad801e6014773229a52707","tid":1183642,"uid":44171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"食垃圾？"},{"pid":"5ebb3c00c701906d34c47d0cba77df8d4d5d1d9d","tid":1183642,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d67f594e7e8af7130528d345137babec460a13ca","tid":1183642,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rth